<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Holly Willoughby proved she has honed her baking skills through lockdown after sharing a space-themed rainbow cake dedicated to her 'dear friend Moon Man'. </p>

<p>The This Morning presenter, 39, shared a picture of red, yellow, green and blue cake batter in polka-dot dishes as she baked with her children, Harry, 11, Belle, nine and Chester, five, on Saturday. </p>

